game.base
Class PhysicsGame

java.lang.Object
  game.base.PhysicsGame
Direct Known Subclasses:
GraphicalWorld
public abstract class PhysicsGame
extends java.lang.Object

Implementation of a game loop for a physics based game.

This class defines a pure high speed game loop that runs as fast as CPU/GPU will allow

Author:
Salvatore Loria Giuseppe Leone, Andrea Martire.
